tool_description:
an API that returns current Disc Golf World Rankings. 

Data includes player name, dominance index, and udisclive.com profile. Includes male and female disc golf players.
name: Current Disc Golf World Rankings
title: Current Disc Golf World Rankings

api_list.name: Get Womens's Rankings
api_list.description: This endpoint will return back data from the DGPT including player name, rank, rating,  & udisclive.com profile URL.
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://current-disc-golf-world-rankings.p.rapidapi.com/dgpt-rankings-women"

headers = {
            "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
            "X-RapidAPI-Host": "current-disc-golf-world-rankings.p.rapidapi.com"
        }

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)
print(response.json())
